snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 03 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Nisa Cosmetics - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 03 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 4th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa Cosmetics

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

#TereBinEP03
#YumnaZaidi
#Wahajali 
#Nisacosmetics

snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Part 1 : Ek Se Bhali Do - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Duolingo and learn any language for free - https://app.adjust.net.in/jgl36j4

Ye life achche achchon ko halaal kar deti hain lekin hamare Rinku ki kahani thodi different hain. Isne khud ja ke musibat se panga liya. Rinku ki life mast chal rahi thi. Bade sheher mein sarkari naukari ki tayyari kar raha tha aur ek girlfriend bhi thi, Raveena, jo isse apna naukar samajhti thi Par phir bhi Rinku apne roommate Neetu ke sath khush tha. Phir iski life mein aayi Sangeeta aur life mein 5th gear lag gaya. Ek ke baad ek kamaal hone laga aur apna Rinku halaal hone laga. Yakeen na ho to khud dekh lo. Ek aisi kahani jis mein music hai, drama hai, action hai ( Rinku ki life mein ) , romance hai aur bahut saari confusion ke sath double dose of comedy bhi hai. Full family ke sath enjoy this special presentation

snippet.description:
#currentaffairs2022 #currentaffairsrevision #kumargauravsir 

Maha Episode 💥 | Current Affairs 2022 January to December | Kumar Gaurav Sir | Utkarsh Classes 

📢"महा एपिसोड🔥 वार्षिकांक लॉन्च" 
2022 के करेंट अफेयर्स का सूपड़ा साफ़।
जी हाँ, नव वर्ष के प्रथम दिन को पढ़ाई के नजरिए से यादगार बनाने के लिए कुमार सर अपने प्यारे शेर, शेरनियों के लिए 2022 के करेंट अफेयर्स का एक ही क्लास में सूपड़ा साफ़ करने के लिए पूरे जोश और जुनून के साथ ले रहें हैं और “करेंट अफेयर्स वार्षिकांक-2022” की विशेष सौगात भी साथ 3 यानी नए साल के पहले ही दिन खुशियों का डबल डोज।
तो, 1 Jan 2023 की शाम को 7 बजे जुड़ने से बिल्कुल भी चूकिएगा मत, क्योंकि इस क्लास के माध्यम से 2022 का सम्पूर्ण करेंट अफेयर्स होने वाला है आपकी मुट्ठी में।

2022 के करेंट अफेयर्स का सूपड़ा साफ़।
जी हाँ, नव वर्ष के प्रथम दिन को पढ़ाई के नजरिए से यादगार बनाने के लिए कुमार सर अपने प्यारे शेर, शेरनियों के लिए 2022 के करेंट अफेयर्स का एक ही क्लास में सूपड़ा साफ़ करने के लिए पूरे जोश और जुनून के साथ ले रहें हैं और “करेंट अफेयर्स वार्षिकांक-2022” की विशेष सौगात भी साथ 3 यानी नए साल के पहले ही दिन खुशियों का डबल डोज।

snippet.title: Every Indian Wedding Ever | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys
This Video shows all the crazy fun that happens in Big Fat Indian weddings. Relatives giving advices about marriage. All the money , gifts , wedding preps , indian food , gol gappe , tikki , chart items , Paneer Tikka ,  spicy food , indian sweets , shaadi lehenga , bride makeup , wedding shopping , crazy dancing on wedding songs . Indian aunties taking lime light . Mehendi functions getting henna done and celebrating with family , friends , cousins . Ldki Wale vs ladke Wale , wedding photographers , pharo time and shadi wali coffee and crying on bidai , attending Big Fat Indian weddings like Kohli Tents , Flying Drones in weddings , Grand , Indian Bride entry with russians arounds , Wide variety of Indian Wedding Tasty food , malai chaap to gulab jamun , jalebi rabri , ice cream , Kids wearing skivi sweater under lehenga to deal with winter weddings , the struggles of Rishta before Marraige , Dealing with dowry , Every Girls struugles , Indian mom and super excited for daughter wedding , dreaming about grandchidlren , her beti being a maa one day , buying and placing a lot indian snacks daal kachori , samosa , pakore , dry fruits & nuts , barati ready for baraat dance on dhol , tired from 7 days of shadi functions , haldi , cocktail , sangeet , god tikka , mehendi , god bharai , halwai at home , indian relatives and theri demands , exclusive parlour makeup , hd bridal makeup , celebrity makeup , airbrush makeup , glitter makeup , high wedding makeup and hairstyle prices , wonder ladies with babies in wedding and doing rasams , dealing traffic jam while reaching a shaadi , every girls efforts of getting in lehenga , jhumka , doing makeup and then getting out of lehenga , removing heavy layers of makeup before sleeping , removing jwelery bangles , high heels , going on honeymoon and celebrating New Year goa , newyork , paris , london , switerland , enjoying bhaji , mathi achar , bondi ladoo , with tea or masala Chai , Going to Chandi Chowk for bridal shopping , choosing from wide variety of Bride lehenga color choices , red , maroon , pink , blue , green , trying different designs sabyasachi , manish malhotra , celebrity bridal lehengas , lehenga from jaipur with heavy embroidery work , crazy lehenga shopkeppers , high prices of lehenga and bargaining in that , bride not able to diet near marraige eating outside food golgappe to curb with full day of wedding shopping , after wedding counting money got from shagun , decorating gold daimond jewelry in front of indian guest buidling new homes before marraige , saas bahu happy in their new mother daughter relationship , kids mesmerized by new bhabhi and her makeup kit . 
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in an indian wedding.  
Relish and Relive your Memories.. You will have major nostalgia .
Do share it with your friends , family , Relatives and Cousins .. A Very Happy New Year Guys 
Comment down your Fav Part, 
Like, Share and

snippet.title: వెన్నలా కరిగిపోయే గోదారొళ్ల సంక్రాంతి స్పెషల్ కొబ్బరి పాకుండలు |Perfect Pakundalu recipe @VismaiFood
snippet.description:
Are you looking for a delicious and easy recipe to make Perfect Bellam Pakundalu? Look no further! In this video, I'll show you how to make this delicious and unique dish using simple ingredients that you likely have on hand.

This pakundalu recipe is a sankranthi special recipe in the coastal region of Andhra Pradesh, especially the Godavari districts and uttharandhras. It's a unique and delicious dish that everyone will love. If you're looking for a dish that will show off your cooking skills, this is the recipe for you!

भाज्या चिरताना या गोष्टी माहिती असायलाच हव्यात | स्वयंपाकात उपयोगी 10 किचन टिप्स Useful Kitchen Tips
बऱ्याच वेळा स्वयंपाक घरात काम करत असताना काही गोष्टी खूप सोप्या असतात पण माहीत नसल्याने आपण करत नाही किंवा अवघड पद्धतीने करतो. काही नवशिके, नव्याने स्वयंपाक शिकणारी मुले, नवीन लग्न झालेल्या मुली यांना या गोष्टी अवघड जातात. नव्याने स्वयंपाक शिकणाऱ्यांसाठी किचन टिप्स, किचन टिप्स, किचन उपयुक्त महत्वाच्या किचन टिप्स. यावर आधीच विडियो बनवले आहेत, पण आज आपण स्वयंपाक करत असताना भाज्या कशा चिराव्यात ही पाहणार आहोत. कांदा बारीक कसं कापावा कोबी कसा कापावा? व्हेज कटलेट साथी भजया कश्या कापाव्यात? ही समजत नाहीत. इथे मी सोप्या पद्धती सांगितल्या आहेत. तुमचे स्वयंपाकतील कामे सोपी होतील. स्वयंपाक करताना उशीर होतो? पसारा होतो? मग हा विडियो शेवटपर्यंत नक्की पहा. सुगरण होण्यासाठी या गोष्टी माहिती असायलाच हव्यात. 
सुगरण होण्यासाठी या 10 गोष्टी माहिती असायलाच हव्यात. या महत्वपूर्ण 10 किचन टिप्स मी संगत आहे. तुम्हाला नक्कीच उपयुक्त येतील. 

गाजर किसायचा कंटाळा येतो? कुकरमध्ये चिकट न होता दाणेदार गाजर हलवा दीड किलो प्रमाण1 ट्रिक Gajar Halwa https://youtu.be/F6O94GPNHG4

खमंग तीळाची पोळी। या 7 टिप्स वापरून बनवा 8 दिवस टिकणारी कडेपर्यंत सारण पसरून खुसखुशीत तीळ गूळ पोळी  https://youtu.be/E6xtq4FoXuI

स्वयंपाक करताना या गोष्टी माहित असायलाच हव्यात | स्वयंपाकात उपयोगी 10 किचन टिप्स Useful Kitchen Tips https://youtu.be/yxVnWjk3obc



Today in SaritasKitchen we are going to see how to chop vegetables in correct way. We are going to see 10 useful kitchen tips to make our daily life easy. To make tasty food and you can complete cooking in less time.

snippet.title: Bihaan के साथ हुआ हादसा | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 582
snippet.description:
To download the Voot app please click on the link: https://voot.onelink.me/eIb4/9b2f5423

To subscribe to this channel, go to: https://www.youtube.com/c/ColorsRishtey1/featured

Watching Thapki leave, Bihaan follows her on the bike and meets with an accident. Is Shraddha responsible for this? Seven years pass by, Sankar and Shraddha now rule the Pandey house and ill-treat Thapki's daughter, Tina. Will Thapki and Bihaan ever return to the Pandey household? 

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 04 Teaser - 4th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 04 Teaser - 4th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Lakadbaggha - Official Trailer | Anshuman Jha, Ridhi Dogra, Milind Soman & Paresh Pahuja | 13th Jan
snippet.description:
Music 👉🏻 SUBSCRIBE to Zee Music Company - https://bit.ly/2yPcBkS 

Animal Lover Vigilante vs Animal Abuser Kingpin.

Present Day - “Street dogs across Kolkata are disappearing” - An antagonist runs a crazy wicked agency using the Kolkata port to sell animals - from rare turtles to (extinct) birds - but on the side also takes up illegal contracts from middle class bengali "bhodroloks" (Gen-tlemen) to take out "disturbing" street dogs.

A protagonist, who lets his punches and flying kicks (Krav-Maga) do all the talking and becomes the much needed voice of our turmoiled co-habitants (Dogs) on the planet. But it ain’t just an action movie.

Cast - Anshuman Jha, Ridhi Dogra, Paresh Pahuja & Milind Soman
Production House - First Ray Films
Producer - Anshuman Jha
Director - Victor Mukherjee
DOP - Jean Marc Selva (AFC)
Music - Simon Fransquet
Writer - Alok Sharma
Action Director - Jaika Stunts (Kecha Khamphakdee) & Force Square
Singers - Shruti Pathak & Epr Iyer
Editor - Aasif Pathan
Production Design - Shantanu Chatterjee

snippet.description:
Team CID was surprised to see Purvi married to a weird man. Later they get involved in a case where a married couple is trapped by a man. Team CID gets involved to save the lives of this couple. To know more watch the full episode.

Show Name: CID 
Show Cast & Characters: 
• Shivaji Satam as ACP Pradyuman
• Dinesh Phadnis as Inspector Fredricks aka Freddy
• Ashutosh Gowariker as Sr. Inspector Virendra
• Dayanand Shetty as Sr. Inspector Daya
• Narendra Gupta as Dr. R. P. Salunkhe
• Aditya Srivastava as Sr. Inspector Abhijeet
• Shraddha Musale as Dr. Tarika
• Ansha Sayed as Sub-Inspector Purvi
Episode: 1495
Producer: Brijendra Pal Singh

#CID #livcrime #सीआईडी #NewCID #LatestCID

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Crime: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCzXpAx4v6rFLYXkJZ5nmSvQ?sub_confirmation=1

About CID:
-----------------
The first thrilling investigative series on Indian Television is today one of the most popular shows on Sony Entertainment Television. Dramatic and absolutely unpredictable, C.I.D. has captivated viewers over the last eleven years and continues to keep audiences glued to their television sets with its thrilling plots and excitement. Also interwoven in its fast-paced plots are the personal challenges that the C.I.D. team faces with non-stop adventure, tremendous pressure, and risk, all in the name of duty. The series consists of hard-core police procedural stories dealing with investigation, detection, and suspense. The protagonists of the serial are an elite group of police officers belonging to the Crime Investigation Department of the police force, led by ACP Pradyuman [played by the dynamic Shivaji Satam]. While the stories are plausible, there is an emphasis on dramatic plotting and technical complexities faced by the police. At every stage, the plot throws up intriguing twists and turns to keep the officers on the move as they track criminals, led by the smallest of clues.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3659 - 4 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3659: Bagha Has Good News For Jetha
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha tries to explain the significance of Bhide's written thoughts on the bulletin board of society. The children are perplexed by his explanations, so Iyer steps in and explains the true meaning. He also talks about the importance of the Sanskrit language. Iyer discusses the Rishis who mentioned "Brahmastra," the most powerful weapon, in Sanskrit scriptures. Later, Bagha rushes into the shop, claiming to have some exciting news for his boss, Jetha. Watch the episode to learn more!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3659, 4 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000203086

snippet.title: Paneer Butter Masala | होटल जैसा पनीर बटर मसाला | Restaurant Style | Chef Sanjyot Keer
snippet.description:
Full  written recipe for Paneer Butter Masala

Prep time: 10-15 minutes
Cooking time: 20-25 minutes
Serves: 4-5 people

Ingredients:
Paste
TOMATO | टमाटर 4 NOS. 
GARLIC | लेहसुन 8-10 CLOVES. 
GINGER | अदरक 1 INCH
CORIANDER STEMS | धनिया के डंठल 2 TBSP
GREEN CHILLI | हरी मिर्च 1 NO. 
KASHMIRI / DEGI RED CHILLI POWDER | कश्मीरी / देगी लाल मिर्च पाउडर 1.5 TBSP
CORIANDER POWDER | धनिया पाउडर 1 TBSP
CUMIN POWDER | जीरा पाउडर 1/2 TSP
CASHEW | काजू 15 NOS. (SOAKED)
Paneer sauteing
OIL | तेल 1 TBSP
BUTTER | मक्खन 1 TBSP
PANEER | पनीर 500 GRAMS (CUBED)
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
KASHMIRI RED CHILLI POWDER | कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च पाउडर A PINCH
Final Cooking:
OIL | तेल 2 TBSP
BUTTER | मक्खन 1 TBSP
WHOLE SPICES
CUMIN SEEDS | जीरा 1 TSP
GREEN CARDAMOM | हरी इलायची 3 NOS. 
CINNAMON | दालचीनी 1/2 INCH
BAY LEAF | तेज पत्ता 1 NO. 
GARLIC | लेहसुन 1 TBSP (CHOPPED)
GREEN CHILLI | हरी मिर्च 1 NO. (CHOPPED)
ONION | प्याज़ 3 MEDIUM SIZED (CHOPPED)
TURMERIC POWDER | हल्दी पाउडर 1/4 TSP
KASHMIRI RED CHILLI POWDER | कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च पाउडर 1/2 TSP
SALT | नमक TO TASTE
SUGAR | शक्कर A PINCH 
HOT WATER | गरम पानी AS REQUIRED
BUTTER | मक्खन 2 TBSP
ROASTED KASURI METHI POWDER | भुनी हुई कसूरी मेथी पाउडर A PINCH
GARAM MASALA | गरम मसाला A PINCH
FRESH CREAM | फ्रेश क्रीम 3-4 TBSP
FRESH CORIANDER | हरा धनिया AS REQUIRED (CHOPPED)
Method:
Add all the ingredients of the paste into a mixer grinder jar & grind it into a fine paste, make sure you soak the cashews in boiling water for 10-15 minutes before adding it, you can also boil it for 5 minutes.
To sauté the paneer, set a pan over high heat & once it gets hot, add the oil & butter.
Once the oil gets hot, add the cubed paneer, salt & kashmiri red chilli powder, then toss the paneer over high flame for 1-2 minutes, doing this step will help the paneer to hold its structure in the gravy, once sauteed remove the paneer into a bowl & set it aside until you make the gravy.
To make the gravy, heat a wok or a kadhai then add oil & butter, once the oil gets hot, add all the whole spices along with, garlic & chopped green chilli, stir well & then add the onions & cook over medium high flame until the onions turn light golden brown.
Once the onions turn light golden brown add turmeric powder & kashmiri red chilli powder, stir well & then add a splash of hot water, stir well & cook the masala for 2-3 minutes.
Further add the prepared paste along with salt & sugar, stir well & cook over medium high flame until the oil separates.
Once the oil separates add hot water as required to adjust the gravy then cook for 2-3 minutes, then taste the gravy & adjust the seasoning accordingly.
Further add the paneer, butter & all the remaining ingredients, stir well & cook only for 1-2 minutes & then finally sprinkle some more fresh coriander.
Your paneer butter masala is ready, serve hot with naan, tandoori roti or rumali roti.

#YFL #SanjyotKeer #paneerbuttermasala

snippet.title: Marrying A Village Girl Ft. Abhinav Anand & Bhavya Sharma | Webseries | Hasley India
snippet.description:
“Jab pyaar kiya toh darna kya” holds true for every situation that happens when people are in love, be it anything.

Download the inDrive app - https://share.indrive.com/lhG6/sidebyside

Being intimate with someone even if they are your partner has always been a topic that brings awkwardness between people.

And when this happens to a couple who just had an arranged marriage, it becomes worse, kyunki na jaan na pehchaan hum tere mehnaan!

Here with this episode of Side by Side, Hasley India brings to you a story of one such couple who face intimacy issues just because of the fact that they don’t know each other. And when there are these issues, it becomes harder to cope with things.

But instead of every obstacle in their way, how they decide to be with each other, Side by Side; is what makes their bond stronger and special.

Let’s experience this bumpy ride together! Watch the episode till the end.

Farq Episode 20 - [Eng Sub]- Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 3rd January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3658 - 3 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3658: Naye Saal Ka Naya Suvichaar
--------------------------------------------------------
The first day of the year is here, and Bhide is getting some cheery notes from his students. When he reads and listens to them, they make him happy. Even his own student visits him at home and gifts him a rose. Even though Madhavi gives the student some food, he declines and asks her to give him proper breakfast when he visits their house again. At Taarak's home, Jetha asks him to accompany him to have a tasty breakfast, while Anjali confronts them and asks Jetha to have breakfast with them.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3658, 3 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

Click here to subscribe to SAB TV:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000202924

snippet.title: Gokuldham में चल रही है Special Party | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah |Sony Sab Rewind
snippet.description:
Jethalal and his friends return to the Gokuldham Society from the police station. Tappu Sena arranges breakfast for their parents. But is another mess awaiting them? Watch the full episode to find out! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast – Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode No – 2188
Produced By – Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #SAB #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  

Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Click here to enjoy some of the most cherished episodes from 'Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah':
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7aEDVX8XJrhP79i2DeWf6gm

Lyrics 

Sun Soniye Sun Dildar,
Rab Se Bhi Jyada,
Tujhe Karte Hai Pyaar…

Khuda Ki Inayat Hai,
Hamme Jo Milaya Hia,
Diya Pyaar Wala,
Ye Dil Mein Jalaya Hai..
 
Sun Sohniya Sun Dildar,
Rab Se Bhi Jyada,
Tujhe Karte Hai Pyaar…

Tu Hi Khuda Tu Mera Sansar,
Khud Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karti Hoon Pyaar,
Tu Hi Khuda
Tu Mera Sansar,
Khud Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karti Hoon Pyaar..
Lagta Hai Darr Tu Chhod Na Jaaye,
Jaaye To Jaan Sang Le Jaaye..

Dil Ki Hai Dhadkan,
Aakhon Ka Deedar,
Rab Se Bhi Jyada Tujhe,
Karte Hai Pyaar..

Sun Sohniya Sun Dildar,
Rab Se Bhi Jyada,
Tujhe Karte Hai Pyaar…

Khuda Ki Inayat Hai,
Hamme Jo Milaya Hia,
Diya Pyaar Wala,
Ye Dil Mein Jalaya Hai..

Hai Tu saanso Mein ,
Aakhon Mein Mere Yaar,
Khud Se Jyada,
Tujhe Karti Hoon Pyaar…

Tu Hi Khuda Tu Mera Sansar,
Khud Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karti Hoon Pyaar..

Apna Sabse Juda Hum Banayenge,
Pyaari Si Khushiyan Chunke,
Duniya Se Laayenge..

Itna To Kar Mujhpe Aitbaar,
Rabb Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karte Hai Pyaar,
Sun Sohniya Sun Dildar, 
Rab Se Bhi Jyada,
Tujhe Karte Hai Pyaar..

Teri Parchai Se Durr Kaise Jaaungi,
Tujhme Basi Hoon Main,
Tujhme Kho Jaaungi..

Meri Palkon Pe Hai Tera Izhaar,
Khud Se Jyada Tujhe 
Karti Hoon Pyaar…

snippet.description:
Why are Indian roads so UNSAFE?
In this video we will learn about:
1. Types of roads in India
2. Who is responsible for building and maintaining these roads
3. Statistics about accidents in India

Rishabh Pant Accident Reason: अब तक भारतीय क्रिकेटर ऋषभ पंत (Rishabh Pant) के एक्सीडेंट के कई सारे कारण सामने आ चुके हैं लेकिन असल वजह का खुलासा अब हुआ है. उत्तराखंड के मुख्यमंत्री पुष्कर सिंह धामी ने आज (01 जनवरी) मैक्स अस्पताल पहुंचकर उनसे मुलाकात की और हाल चाल जाना. इस दौरान धामी ने सड़क दुर्घटना के कारण को लेकर भी बात की. चलिए आपको बताते हैं आखिर कैसे हुए पंत की कार का एक्सीडेंट. 

सीएम पुष्कर सिंह धामी ने बताया कि इस हादसे को लेकर पंत की मां से उनकी बातचीत हुई थी. उन्होंने बताया कि गड्ढे (Pothole) से बचने के क्रम में ये हादसा हुआ. हालांकि, अब पंत की कंडीशन पहले से काफी बेहतर है. डॉक्टर और बीसीसीआई के लोग भी लगातार उनके संपर्क में हैं. पंत के परिवार वाले भी इलाज से पूरी तरह से संतुष्ट हैं. सीएम ने पंत के जल्द ठीक होने की भी कामना की. 

30 दिसंबर को हुआ सड़क हादसा 

30 दिसंबर को सुबह करीब 5.30 बजे पंत दिल्ली से अपनी मां को सरप्राइज देने के लिए रुड़की लौटते समय एक गंभीर दुर्घटना का शिकार हो गए. इस दौरान उनकी कार हम्मादपुर झाल के पास रुड़की के नारसन बॉर्डर पर डिवाइडर से टकरा गई. वह हादसे के दौरान कार में अकेले थे. इस दौरान उनके पीठ, माथे और पैर में चोटें आई हैं. 

हरियाणा रोडवेज के ड्राइवर-कंडक्टर को सम्मान 

इसके साथ ही सीएम धामी ने गणतंत्र दिवस के मौके पर हरियाणा रोडवेज के ड्राइवर सुशील और कंडक्टर परमजीत को सम्मानित करने का भी एलान किया है. धामी ने कहा कि ड्राइवर और कंडक्टर ने ऋषभ पंत की जान बचाने के लिए अपनी जान जोखिम में डाल दी. अगर सही समय पर मदद नहीं मिली होती तो कुछ भी हो सकता था. बीते दिन उत्तराखंड पुलिस ने भी दोनों को सम्मानित करने की घोषणा की थी. 

Sources:
1 https://www.who.int/news-room/fact-sheets/detail/road-traffic-injuries (General World Overview)
2 https://www.worldbank.org/en/country/india/publication/traffic-crash-injuries-and-disabilities-the-burden-on-indian-society
3 https://blogs.worldbank.org/endpovertyinsouthasia/road-safety-how-state-india-leading-way-lower-road-crash-deaths?cid=sar_tt_india_en_ext
4* https://morth.nic.in/sites/default/files/RA_2020.pdf
5 https://morth.nic.in/sites/default/files/Basic%20Road%20Statistics%20in%20India-2018-19.pdf
6 https://prsindia.org/files/policy/policy_vital_state/Overview%20of%20Road%20Accidents.pdf
7 http://www.bro.gov.in/WriteReadData/linkimages/5768690382-14.pdf
8 https://www.theguardian.com/world/2008/oct/10/india
9 https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/this-is-what-makes-indian-roads-deadliest/articleshow/78870630.cms
10 https://www.deccanherald.com/specials/insight/keeping-people-safe-on-india-s-killer-roads-886704.html
11 https://www.economist.com/asia/2022/08/05/why-indias-roads-are-so-deadly
12 https://www.firstpost.com/india/national-highways-in-south-account-for-most-road-accidents-black-spots-up-tamil-nadu-top-among-states-9848831.html
13 https://www.who.int/publications/i/item/9789241565684
14 https://www.indiatoday.in/diu/story/road-rash-india-accidents-data-2020-1954831-2022-05-27
